具者，處1年以下\r\n有期徒刑、拘役或新臺幣100,000元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1264%2c20220511%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,1264,20220511,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1264","JDATE":"20220511","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}